highlights.text: “Midnight Eyes” by Masters of Prophecy is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #9.
EsDeeKid has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Phantom” is the highest at #17.
“Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 147 days straight.
“Love My Life” by Robbie Williams is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 49 spots at #50.
